{"id":"zibeon","term":"Zibeon","source":"Easton's Bible Dictionary (M.G. Easton, 1897)","html":"<p>Robber; or dyed. (1.) A Hivite (<a class=\"ref\" data-ref=\"Genesis 36:2\">Gen. 36:2</a>).</p>\n<p>(2.) A Horite, and son of Seir (<a class=\"ref\" data-ref=\"Genesis 36:20\">Gen. 36:20</a>).</p>\n\u0000","refs":["Genesis 36:2","Genesis 36:20"]}